OL,3,CAfghans who 'risked their lives'
OL,4,Chelping UK to be housed at Welsh
OL,5,Cmilitary camp
OL,7,FA military camp in Wales will be used
OL,8,Fto house people fleeing the Taliban in
OL,9,FAfghanistan who risked their lives to
OL,10,Fsupport the UK.
OL,12,FEast Camp, a Ministry of Defence (MoD)
OL,13,Fsite at , in the Vale of Glamorgan,
OL,14,Fwill begin accommodating Afghan
OL,15,Ffamilies who are eligible under the
OL,16,FAfghan Relocations and Assistance
OL,17,FPolicy (ARAP) Scheme.
