OL,3,CAfghans who 'risked their lives'
OL,4,Chelping UK to be housed at Welsh
OL,5,Cmilitary camp
OL,7,FThe site will house 50 people by the
OL,8,Fend of the month, with more due to
OL,9,Fjoin in mid-April. The families are
OL,10,Fexpected to stay at the site for
OL,11,Fseveral weeks while their settled
OL,12,Faccommodation on defence estate is
OL,13,Fprepared.
OL,15,FARAP is the MoD's relocation and
OL,16,Fresettlement scheme for Afghans and
OL,17,Ftheir families who worked for, or
OL,18,Fwith, the UK Government and British
OL,19,FArmed Forces in Afghanistan in exposed
OL,20,For meaningful roles, such as acting as
OL,21,Finterpreters or providing intelligence.
