OL,3,CAfghans who 'risked their lives'
OL,4,Chelping UK to be housed at Welsh
OL,5,Cmilitary camp
OL,7,FThe site will be used by families and
OL,8,Fcan host a maximum of 180 people.
OL,9,FThose arriving have a personal
OL,10,Fconnection to the Armed Forces and
OL,11,Fhave indefinite leave to remain.
OL,13,FAfghan families will have access to
OL,14,Fhealthcare when they arrive and the
OL,15,FMoD says that work is underway to
OL,16,Fensure children have access to
OL,17,Feducation.
