OL,3,CAfghans who 'risked their lives'
OL,4,Chelping UK to be housed at Welsh
OL,5,Cmilitary camp
OL,7,FAn MOD Spokesperson said: "We owe a
OL,8,Fdebt of gratitude to those brave
OL,9,FAfghans who risked their lives working
OL,10,Falongside our forces in support of the
OL,11,FUK mission.
OL,13,F"To ensure ARAP eligible families can
OL,14,Fbegin a settled life in the UK as
OL,15,Fquickly as possible, the UK Government
OL,16,Fis offering transitional and settled
OL,17,Faccommodation from the Defence Estate,
OL,18,Fincluding at East Camp St Athan.
